Engagement Data Model

The Customer 360 Data Model engagement subject defines interactions with a party. Example interactions could be speaking to a customer over the phone or receiving a customer email.

The engagement data model includes the individual, contact point, device, and email engagement data model objects.

To view a larger version, right-click or control-click the image and select “Open Image in New Tab” or view the Engagement data model architecture.

These DMOs are represented in the engagement subject area.

DMO	DESCRIPTION	REFERENCE DOC LINK
Device	A Data Cloud DMO for a specific electronic unit that you want to track signals from, for example, a refrigerator, watch, or car.	Device DMO Reference
Device Application Engagement	A Data Cloud DMO for data about device engagement, for example mobile app usage.	Device Application Engagement DMO Reference
Device Application Template	A Data Cloud DMO for a reusable standard format for messages for applications on devices.	Device Application Template DMO Reference
Email Engagement	A Data Cloud DMO for data captured from various data sources about an engagement.	Email Engagement DMO Reference
Email Template	A Data Cloud DMO for the standard form of an email message that can be personalized and customized with data specific to an individual recipient, market segment, or other customization factor.	Email Template DMO Reference
Engagement Topic	A Data Cloud DMO for engagement topics such as multiple campaigns or promotions.	Engagement Topic DMO Reference
Product Browse Engagement	A Data Cloud DMO for data captured from a user action, such as searching for products or viewing a list of products.	Product Browse Engagement DMO Reference
Product Order Engagement	A Data Cloud DMO for a user’s online shopping order data.	Product Order Engagement DMO Reference
Shopping Cart Engagement	A Data Cloud DMO for data captured from user actions, such as adding and removing items from a shopping cart.	Shopping Cart Engagement DMO Reference
SMS Engagement	A Data Cloud DMO for data captured from various data sources about a message engagement.	
SMS Template	A Data Cloud DMO for a reusable, standard format for text (SMS) messages.	SMS Template DMO Reference
Web Search Engagement	A Data Cloud DMO for web search engagement data. 	Web Search Engagement DMO Reference
Website Engagement	A Data Cloud DMO for any data associated with website engagement, like views or clicks.	Website Engagement DMO Reference
